<h1>Welcome to the FOX TRIAL FINDER CHALLENGE</h1>
<p class="intro">The Michael J. Fox Foundation (MJFF) is challenging clinical research sites around the country to refer volunteers to sign up for Fox Trial Finder. Register by December 31, 2013 to help a site near you win a complimentary event open to the PD community featuring PD research updates and a presentation by a member of the MJFF staff.</p>
<h2 style="margin-top: 1em;" class="orange">Help your site win by registering on Fox Trial Finder today!</h2>
